                                <h1>Bing Search Redesign - Weather</h1>
                                <p>
                                        Searching the weather using search engines is common, but the motivation and goals of such behavior are different from using the mobile phone APP to check the weather. Taking into account the great advantages of search engines in information accumulation about both the user and the weather, the weather answer can be strongly personalized. </br>
                                        By analyzing the possible scenarios where users would use search engines to check the weather,I decide to focus on helping users to check the weather where they might arrive in the future and helping them to analyze weather in different cities to make plans as well as giving them direct suggestion.
                                    </p>
                            </div>
